query:
INSERT INTO server (
        user_id,
        project_id,
        cloud_id,
        region,
        zone,
        server,
        os,
        disk_type,
        created_at,
        updated_at,
        srv_ip,
        ssh_user,
        ssh_port,
        vault_key_path,
        connection_mode,
        key_status,
        name
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, NOW() at time zone 'utc',NOW() at time zone 'utc', $9, $10, $11, $12, $13, $14, $15)
        RETURNING id;
